description.value: This value set Includes concepts that represent pregnancy related procedures.

purpose.value: The purpose of this value set is to represent types of procedures performed during pregnancy.

copyright.value: Please see NLM VSAC (https://vsac.nlm.nih.gov/) for the latest version of the value sets: Procedures during Pregnancy (CPT) 2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.111.11.1014 and Procedures during Pregnancy (SNOMED-CT) 2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.111.11.1015
